reviews.review_text:
Firsts First Saint of Circumstance without Lost Sailor preceding it. Also, Garcia plays the Cornell alma mater during the first "Take A Step Back" after Jack Straw.
Peace, Bob
english country garden and during the second "take a step back",Mr. Garcia nicely notes out a fine rendering of English Country Garden.5 stars to the party
